{% set active='about' %}

{% extends "main.html.twig" %}

{% block content %}

<h2>About Lumberjack Phansible</h2>


<p>Lumberjack Phansible is just a customized version of the great <a href="http://phansible.com">Phansible</a>.</p>

<h2>About Phansible</h2>

<p>Phansible is a project created by <a href="http://twitter.com/erikaheidi" target="_blank">Erika Heidi</a> and maintained with collaboration of many <a href="https://github.com/Phansible/phansible/graphs/contributors">contributors</a>. Our goal is to provide
    a tool that is easy to use and still highly customizable, to create <a href="http://vagrantup.com" target="_blank">Vagrant</a>
    provisionings using <a href="http://ansible.com" target="_blank">Ansible</a>.

    Phansible was inspired on <a href="http://puphpet.com" target="_blank">PuPHPet</a>.</p>

<h2>Contributors</h2>
    <p>Many kudos for our contributors!</p>
    <div class="ui raised segment">
        <div class="ui grid">
          {% for dev in contributors %}
            <div class="two wide column contributor-avatar">
                <div class="ui center aligned basic segment">
                  <a href="{{ dev.author.html_url }}" target="_blank"><img src="{{ dev.author.avatar_url }}" class="circular ui small center image"></a>
                  <p><small><a href="{{ dev.author.html_url }}" target="_blank">{{ dev.author.login }}</a></small></p>
                </div>
            </div>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
{% endblock %}
